overview: The Southwestern Assemblies of God University (SAGU) Football team, led by Coach Ryan Smith, is fresh off of a heart breaking defeated season in 2019. The 2020-21 season brings with it the chance to be one of the 5 winningest teams in SAGU history. Follow Coach Smith and a few of his key leaders on and off the field as they fight for redemption.
tagline: TAKE A JOURNEY DOWN THE ROAD TO REDEMPTION
title: Uncommn 2: Road to Redemption
